---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import NodeDecoration from '../components/NodeDecoration.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contatti"
  description="Aiutiamo le aziende a innovare mantenendo il focus su operatività e risultati. Scrivici per parlare del tuo progetto di digitalizzazione."
>

  <section class="contact-hero" style="background: var(--color-dark);">
    <div class="hero__bg-decoration float-soft" aria-hidden="true">
      <NodeDecoration color="rgba(255,96,0,0.10)" animated={true} />
    </div>
    <div class="container contact-hero__content" data-stagger="120">
      <span class="eyebrow" data-animate="fade-up">Parliamone</span>
      <h1 class="contact-hero__title" data-animate="clip-up">Innovazione con i piedi<br>per terra</h1>
      <p class="contact-hero__sub" data-animate="fade-up">
        Aiutiamo le aziende a innovare mantenendo il focus su operatività e risultati.
        Se vuoi confrontarti sul tuo progetto di digitalizzazione, scrivici.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section contact-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid">

        <!-- DIRECT CONTACTS -->
        <div class="contact-direct stagger-list">
          <div class="contact-channel">
            <span class="contact-channel__label">Email</span>
            <a href="mailto:info@ready2digital.it" class="contact-channel__value">info@ready2digital.it</a>
            <span class="contact-channel__note">Ti rispondiamo entro 48 ore.</span>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-channel">
            <span class="contact-channel__label">LinkedIn</span>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maurizio-taruggi-060614241" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-channel__value">Maurizio Taruggi</a>
            <span class="contact-channel__note">Founder &amp; CEO, Ready2Digital</span>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-channel">
            <span class="contact-channel__label">Dove siamo</span>
            <span class="contact-channel__value">Italia</span>
            <span class="contact-channel__note">Lavoriamo con clienti in tutto il Paese.</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- STATEMENT -->
        <aside class="contact-statement" data-animate="fade-left">
          <div class="contact-statement__decoration" aria-hidden="true">
            <NodeDecoration color="rgba(255,96,0,0.12)" animated={true} />
          </div>
          <div class="contact-statement__content">
            <span class="eyebrow">Come lavoriamo</span>
            <p>
              Non vendiamo pacchetti standard. Partiamo sempre dall'obiettivo:
              capire lo stato attuale, mappare i gap, e solo allora individuare
              la soluzione giusta — con il giusto grado di profondità.
            </p>
            <p>
              Se questo modo di pensare ti somiglia, scrivici. Da lì nasce tutto.
            </p>
          </div>
        </aside>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .contact-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding-block: clamp(var(--space-16), 10vw, var(--space-24));
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .hero__bg-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .contact-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .contact-hero__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-4xl), 7vw, var(--text-6xl));
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .contact-hero__sub {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* CONTACT GRID */
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-direct {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  .contact-channel {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-8);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .contact-channel:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact-channel__label {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
  }

  .contact-channel__value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    line-height: 1.1;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  a.contact-channel__value:hover {
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }

  .contact-channel__note {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-gray-mid);
  }

  /* STATEMENT */
  .contact-statement {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-dark);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: var(--space-12);
    min-height: 100%;
  }

  .contact-statement__decoration {
    position: absolute;
    right: -60px;
    top: -60px;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .contact-statement__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .contact-statement .eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-orange);
  }

  .contact-statement p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }
  }
</style>
